1
00:01:37,055 --> 00:01:40,588
[Episode 9]

2
00:01:41,615 --> 00:01:46,074
[Yicheng County]

3
00:01:46,074 --> 00:01:50,375
- Zhan, is this where Zhi Hua ambushed you?
- Yes.

4
00:01:50,375 --> 00:01:52,041
He searched Liu's house,

5
00:01:52,041 --> 00:01:53,975
and didn't find what he wanted,

6
00:01:53,975 --> 00:01:56,441
but he did find the letters between Liu and me.

7
00:01:56,441 --> 00:01:57,941
So he lay in wait,

8
00:01:57,941 --> 00:02:00,090
setting a trap here.

9
00:02:00,090 --> 00:02:01,620
This place has already been searched.

10
00:02:01,620 --> 00:02:04,020
Can we still find any clues?

11
00:02:05,008 --> 00:02:06,675
There's nothing left here,

12
00:02:06,675 --> 00:02:10,965
but Liu Hong Yi's case wouldn't have
just appeared for no reason.

13
00:02:12,140 --> 00:02:13,641
If someone reported the crime,

14
00:02:13,641 --> 00:02:15,541
and the case hasn't been solved yet,

15
00:02:15,541 --> 00:02:18,008
then the victim will surely come back for news.

16
00:02:18,008 --> 00:02:19,341
Exactly.

17
00:02:19,341 --> 00:02:20,735
Once we find the victim,

18
00:02:20,735 --> 00:02:23,690
we can find out how this case started.

19
00:02:24,455 --> 00:02:27,541
There are two shifty-looking watchdogs
stationed at the Liu residence.

20
00:02:27,541 --> 00:02:30,741
They're likely waiting for
the victim to show up too.

21
00:02:30,741 --> 00:02:33,074
Those two idiots gave themselves away long ago.

22
00:02:33,074 --> 00:02:34,475
Still trying to stake it out?

23
00:02:34,475 --> 00:02:36,074
Vegetable sellers only stay
at the alley entrance.

24
00:02:36,074 --> 00:02:38,565
Who wanders around from inside the alley?

25
00:02:43,475 --> 00:02:44,975
Let's wait and see.

26
00:02:44,975 --> 00:02:46,775
See if the victim shows up.

27
00:02:46,775 --> 00:02:48,475
Alright.

28
00:02:48,475 --> 00:02:49,975
I'll go keep watch.

29
00:02:49,975 --> 00:02:52,515
Relieve me in a few hours.

30
00:03:44,055 --> 00:03:46,254
Enjoy your meal, sir.

31
00:03:47,254 --> 00:03:49,421
Anything unusual?

32
00:03:50,421 --> 00:03:51,688
Be patient.

33
00:03:51,688 --> 00:03:53,121
They're still there.

34
00:03:53,121 --> 00:03:55,055
It means they haven't found the victim either.

35
00:03:55,055 --> 00:03:57,102
Let's wait a bit longer.

36
00:04:02,455 --> 00:04:05,777
That peddler has been walking back and forth.

37
00:04:11,335 --> 00:04:13,581
He just paces without calling out.

38
00:04:13,581 --> 00:04:16,048
How can he sell anything like that?

39
00:04:16,048 --> 00:04:18,652
Could he be from the magistrate's office?

40
00:04:20,081 --> 00:04:22,523
He's not.

41
00:04:34,081 --> 00:04:35,640
Wake up.

42
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:37,752
It's him again.

43
00:04:39,081 --> 00:04:40,465
Let's go, take a look.

44
00:04:40,465 --> 00:04:41,535
Come and have a look!

45
00:04:41,535 --> 00:04:44,214
Folks, I'd like to ask you something.

46
00:04:44,214 --> 00:04:48,448
Have you heard of a scholar named
Liu living on this street?

47
00:04:48,448 --> 00:04:51,081
How are you related to him?
Why are you looking for him?

48
00:04:52,081 --> 00:04:54,048
Our relationship is quite complex.

49
00:04:54,048 --> 00:04:56,620
He is my cousin's husband's...

50
00:04:56,620 --> 00:04:58,380
cousin's son's aunt's brother.

51
00:04:58,380 --> 00:05:00,743
I heard he struck it rich
and moved to this town two years ago.

52
00:05:00,743 --> 00:05:03,341
I came all this way
just to ask him for a favor.

53
00:05:03,341 --> 00:05:06,341
My cousin's husband's cousin is in trouble.

54
00:05:06,341 --> 00:05:08,241
His face is covered in a rash.
It's quite terrifying!

55
00:05:08,241 --> 00:05:10,460
I'm worried if he isn't treated,
he won't be able to leave the house.

56
00:05:10,460 --> 00:05:13,220
- The rash is all over his face--
- Move along, move along!

57
00:05:13,220 --> 00:05:14,575
Stop causing trouble here, okay?

58
00:05:14,575 --> 00:05:16,241
You could just say you don't know.

59
00:05:16,241 --> 00:05:17,475
Why are you shooing me away?

60
00:05:17,475 --> 00:05:19,502
Where did he go?

61
00:05:33,408 --> 00:05:34,541
Who are you?

62
00:05:34,541 --> 00:05:37,008
The magistrate's men have spotted you already.

63
00:05:37,008 --> 00:05:39,390
You'll be arrested if you go back.

64
00:05:43,075 --> 00:05:44,975
Are you looking for Officer Liu?

65
00:05:44,975 --> 00:05:46,939
How did you know?

66
00:05:47,674 --> 00:05:48,990
This jade pendant...

67
00:05:48,990 --> 00:05:51,163
It belongs to Liu.

68
00:05:54,441 --> 00:05:55,808
Yes.

69
00:05:55,808 --> 00:05:58,075
Officer Liu said if anything happened to him,

70
00:05:58,075 --> 00:05:59,674
I should keep this pendant with me.

71
00:05:59,674 --> 00:06:03,374
Someone would recognize it and come to meet me.

72
00:06:03,374 --> 00:06:06,674
So you are... Lord Zhan?

73
00:06:06,674 --> 00:06:08,041
I am Zhan Zhao.

74
00:06:08,041 --> 00:06:09,208
I serve at Kaifeng Prefecture.

75
00:06:09,208 --> 00:06:12,220
I am Liu's sworn brother.

76
00:06:12,220 --> 00:06:14,100
Lord Zhan!

77
00:06:15,174 --> 00:06:16,874
My sister has been missing for days.

78
00:06:16,874 --> 00:06:19,008
Officer Liu was helping me search for her,

79
00:06:19,008 --> 00:06:20,374
but then he met with a tragic end.

80
00:06:20,374 --> 00:06:22,041
His death is truly suspicious.

81
00:06:22,041 --> 00:06:23,741
Please Lord Zhan...

82
00:06:23,741 --> 00:06:26,608
get justice for Officer Liu and my sister!

83
00:06:27,608 --> 00:06:29,041
This is no place to talk.

84
00:06:29,041 --> 00:06:31,177
Maybe we should go inside.

85
00:06:40,741 --> 00:06:42,241
Come on.

86
00:06:50,671 --> 00:06:52,177
So you're not a peddler,

87
00:06:52,177 --> 00:06:54,441
but a scholar.

88
00:06:54,441 --> 00:06:56,408
But why are you living here?

89
00:06:56,408 --> 00:06:59,575
I used to live in a house on Xinghua Street.

90
00:06:59,575 --> 00:07:01,408
After Constable Liu's incident,

91
00:07:01,408 --> 00:07:03,408
the bailiffs sealed off my house.

92
00:07:03,408 --> 00:07:05,286
Fortunately, I wasn't home at the time.

93
00:07:05,286 --> 00:07:06,441
So I escaped a disaster.

94
00:07:06,441 --> 00:07:07,874
Are you writing a petition?

95
00:07:07,874 --> 00:07:09,340
Yes.

96
00:07:09,340 --> 00:07:13,341
Constable Liu was implicated
because of my sister and me.

97
00:07:13,341 --> 00:07:15,270
I can't let him die without getting justice.

98
00:07:15,270 --> 00:07:16,765
I'm going to report this to the court office.

99
00:07:16,765 --> 00:07:18,374
Clear his name.

100
00:07:18,374 --> 00:07:21,141
I didn't expect a scholar like you
to be so courageous.

101
00:07:21,141 --> 00:07:24,865
You're thinking about others
when your own life is at risk.

102
00:07:24,865 --> 00:07:25,874
What is your name?

103
00:07:25,874 --> 00:07:28,141
My name is Fan Zhong Yu.

104
00:07:28,141 --> 00:07:29,841
[Fan Zhong Yu]
My parents died when I was young.

105
00:07:29,841 --> 00:07:32,475
My sister, Yu Lian, and I have only each other.

106
00:07:32,475 --> 00:07:34,041
Fan.

107
00:07:34,041 --> 00:07:35,374
About Yu Lian's case,

108
00:07:35,374 --> 00:07:37,841
please tell me in detail.

109
00:07:38,841 --> 00:07:41,677
After I passed the imperial exam,

110
00:07:41,677 --> 00:07:44,174
Yu Lian was very happy for me.

111
00:07:44,174 --> 00:07:47,874
In order to save enough money for me
to study at Xiangyang Academy,

112
00:07:47,874 --> 00:07:50,341
she quit her job
at the Yicheng Embroidery Shop,

113
00:07:50,341 --> 00:07:51,874
and started embroidering at home.

114
00:07:51,874 --> 00:07:55,075
She said the embroidery shops in Xiangyang
paid a higher price.

115
00:07:55,075 --> 00:07:58,008
So, she often went to Xiangyang
to sell her patterns.

116
00:07:58,008 --> 00:07:59,855
Brother, I'm leaving now.

117
00:07:59,855 --> 00:08:01,461
The prices at the Xiangyang shops
have gone up again.

118
00:08:01,461 --> 00:08:03,790
Wait, Yu Lian!

119
00:08:05,075 --> 00:08:07,141
I don't necessarily have to
go to Xiangyang Academy.

120
00:08:07,141 --> 00:08:08,775
But I want you to go.

121
00:08:08,775 --> 00:08:11,728
When you pass the high exam,
I'll enjoy a good life.

122
00:08:11,728 --> 00:08:13,702
I'm off, Brother!

123
00:08:13,702 --> 00:08:16,275
About two months ago,

124
00:08:16,275 --> 00:08:18,341
after Yu Lian went to Xiangyang,

125
00:08:18,341 --> 00:08:20,374
she never came back.

126
00:08:20,374 --> 00:08:22,241
After searching in Xiangyang for three days,

127
00:08:22,241 --> 00:08:25,208
I reported it to the county magistrate,
but there was never any news.

128
00:08:25,208 --> 00:08:28,341
I went back to ask several times,
but they said they hadn't found her.

129
00:08:28,341 --> 00:08:30,674
Later on, they got annoyed
by my constant asking.

130
00:08:30,674 --> 00:08:33,208
They kicked me out and even beat me up!

131
00:08:33,208 --> 00:08:36,608
They wouldn't help
and even beat the person reporting.

132
00:08:36,608 --> 00:08:38,341
What kind of justice is that?

133
00:08:38,341 --> 00:08:39,808
They warned me.

134
00:08:39,808 --> 00:08:41,774
That if I wanted to live...

135
00:08:41,774 --> 00:08:43,774
I should stop pestering the magistrate.

136
00:08:43,774 --> 00:08:45,941
That day, they beat me half to death.

137
00:08:45,941 --> 00:08:48,541
It was Constable Liu who intervened
and saved me,

138
00:08:48,541 --> 00:08:49,808
and treated my wounds.

139
00:08:49,808 --> 00:08:51,541
After learning the whole story,

140
00:08:51,541 --> 00:08:54,041
Constable Liu said he would take the case.

141
00:08:54,041 --> 00:08:55,641
He would help me find Yu Lian.

142
00:08:55,641 --> 00:08:56,975
Liu Hong Yi...

143
00:08:56,975 --> 00:08:59,475
he had just been transferred to Yicheng County.

144
00:08:59,475 --> 00:09:05,374
I suppose he could no longer tolerate
the actions of the Yicheng County Magistrate.

145
00:09:05,374 --> 00:09:08,075
Otherwise, as a mere constable...

146
00:09:08,075 --> 00:09:10,441
he wouldn't have taken this case
without authorization.

147
00:09:10,441 --> 00:09:13,241
Constable Liu told me not to count
on the Yicheng Magistrate.

148
00:09:13,241 --> 00:09:14,841
He said he would give me justice.

149
00:09:14,841 --> 00:09:17,041
About ten days later,

150
00:09:17,041 --> 00:09:20,241
he said he had a lead on Yu Lian's whereabouts.

151
00:09:20,241 --> 00:09:22,241
But he said the case was very dangerous.

152
00:09:22,241 --> 00:09:24,641
He asked a friend from Kaifeng Prefecture
to come and help.

153
00:09:24,641 --> 00:09:25,975
He told me to wait for news at home,

154
00:09:25,975 --> 00:09:28,441
and warned me not to go looking for him.

155
00:09:28,441 --> 00:09:30,975
He also told me not to tell anyone
that I knew him.

156
00:09:30,975 --> 00:09:32,241
Later on...

157
00:09:32,241 --> 00:09:34,208
my... my house was sealed off.

158
00:09:34,208 --> 00:09:37,095
Lord Zhan, I was afraid you wouldn't find me,

159
00:09:37,095 --> 00:09:42,036
so I disguised myself as a peddler
to keep watch near Constable Liu's house.

160
00:09:44,241 --> 00:09:46,075
Are those all he said?

161
00:09:46,075 --> 00:09:49,408
He didn't give you any other clues?

162
00:09:49,408 --> 00:09:51,208
At the time...

163
00:09:51,208 --> 00:09:54,874
I was so worried about my sister's safety
that I wanted to ask more questions.

164
00:09:54,874 --> 00:09:57,608
But Constable Liu said for my own safety,

165
00:09:57,608 --> 00:10:00,341
he couldn't say too much.

166
00:10:00,341 --> 00:10:01,934
In the letter he sent me,

167
00:10:01,934 --> 00:10:03,208
he only mentioned...

168
00:10:03,208 --> 00:10:05,408
there was a major case in Xiangzhou
that needed my help.

169
00:10:05,408 --> 00:10:07,374
He didn't mention anything else.

170
00:10:07,374 --> 00:10:11,952
He was afraid the letter might fall into
the wrong hands and put you in danger.

171
00:10:11,952 --> 00:10:15,175
Constable Liu was dragged into this
because of my sister and me.

172
00:10:15,175 --> 00:10:16,675
That is why he was murdered.

173
00:10:16,675 --> 00:10:19,236
I have truly failed him.

174
00:10:20,075 --> 00:10:21,374
Fan.

175
00:10:21,374 --> 00:10:22,774
Do not blame yourself.

176
00:10:22,774 --> 00:10:24,241
Liu was a man of the law.

177
00:10:24,241 --> 00:10:25,702
His lifelong ideal

178
00:10:25,702 --> 00:10:27,374
was to seek justice for the people.

179
00:10:27,374 --> 00:10:29,027
He would never regret taking this case.

180
00:10:29,027 --> 00:10:31,874
Now, if we want to avenge him,

181
00:10:31,874 --> 00:10:33,300
the only way

182
00:10:33,300 --> 00:10:35,475
is to finish the investigation for him,

183
00:10:35,475 --> 00:10:37,876
and find your sister's whereabouts.

184
00:10:38,741 --> 00:10:40,390
Fan, you just said...

185
00:10:40,390 --> 00:10:41,900
Yu Lian went to Xiangyang

186
00:10:41,900 --> 00:10:43,970
to sell her embroidery.

187
00:10:43,970 --> 00:10:46,103
Did you ever search the
embroidery shops in Xiangyang?

188
00:10:46,103 --> 00:10:49,380
I have searched every embroidery shop.

189
00:10:49,380 --> 00:10:52,327
But they all said they hadn't seen her.

190
00:10:52,327 --> 00:10:55,274
Could something have happened
on the way to Xiangyang?

191
00:10:55,274 --> 00:10:56,841
It is hard to say.

192
00:10:56,841 --> 00:10:59,941
Fan, which embroidery shop did
Yu Lian frequent most?

193
00:10:59,941 --> 00:11:01,808
It's called Ruzhen Embroidery Shop.

194
00:11:01,808 --> 00:11:04,041
Because that shop offered the highest prices,

195
00:11:04,041 --> 00:11:05,641
Yu Lian went there often.

196
00:11:05,641 --> 00:11:07,208
But I went there to ask several times,

197
00:11:07,208 --> 00:11:09,141
and they were very impatient with me.

198
00:11:09,141 --> 00:11:12,408
They told me to stop disturbing their business.

199
00:11:12,408 --> 00:11:13,975
Let's set off.

200
00:11:13,975 --> 00:11:17,374
Go investigate Ruzhen Embroidery Shop.

201
00:11:17,374 --> 00:11:20,690
I will go with you. I can lead the way.

202
00:11:20,690 --> 00:11:21,727
Alright.

203
00:11:21,727 --> 00:11:23,408
- But...
- No buts.

204
00:11:23,408 --> 00:11:24,502
I will look after him.

205
00:11:24,502 --> 00:11:26,543
You focus on the case.

206
00:11:28,175 --> 00:11:32,243
Can you describe Yu Lian's appearance?
It will make it easier to find her.

207
00:11:40,860 --> 00:11:44,860
[Xiangyang City]

208
00:11:55,741 --> 00:11:57,740
This way.

209
00:12:05,975 --> 00:12:08,075
[Ruzhen Embroidery Shop]
This is Ruzhen Embroidery Shop.

210
00:12:08,075 --> 00:12:09,586
When I first came,

211
00:12:09,586 --> 00:12:11,133
they just said they hadn't seen Yu Lian.

212
00:12:11,133 --> 00:12:12,408
They told me to leave at once.

213
00:12:12,408 --> 00:12:13,874
When I came back a second time,

214
00:12:13,874 --> 00:12:16,774
I saw a small door behind the counter
that leads to the backyard.

215
00:12:16,774 --> 00:12:19,408
I asked if I could take a look at the backyard.

216
00:12:19,408 --> 00:12:22,374
But the shopkeeper suddenly
got violent and punched me.

217
00:12:22,374 --> 00:12:24,208
Then he had me thrown out.

218
00:12:24,208 --> 00:12:25,208
Don't worry.

219
00:12:25,208 --> 00:12:27,041
I'll definitely return that punch for you.

220
00:12:27,041 --> 00:12:29,641
But when the three of us go in later,
you don't have to follow us.

221
00:12:29,641 --> 00:12:32,374
You've been here twice.
They'll be on guard the moment they see you.

222
00:12:32,374 --> 00:12:35,041
It'll make things difficult for us.

223
00:12:35,041 --> 00:12:37,441
Two grown men entering an embroidery shop
is too conspicuous.

224
00:12:37,441 --> 00:12:38,941
I should be the one to go.

225
00:12:38,941 --> 00:12:41,990
Young Mistress, have you ever been to one?

226
00:12:41,990 --> 00:12:44,441
Oh? As if you have?

227
00:12:44,441 --> 00:12:47,265
I have my ways.

228
00:12:57,008 --> 00:12:58,840
Stop fanning.

229
00:13:04,855 --> 00:13:07,075
[Ruzhen Embroidery Shop]

230
00:13:24,141 --> 00:13:25,175
Shopkeeper!

231
00:13:25,175 --> 00:13:27,700
Bring out all your best

232
00:13:27,700 --> 00:13:30,374
silk threads and embroidery!

233
00:13:30,374 --> 00:13:31,841
What are you dazed for?

234
00:13:31,841 --> 00:13:35,915
Hurry up and bring out our finest goods!

235
00:13:39,208 --> 00:13:41,208
Sir, please wait a moment.

236
00:13:41,208 --> 00:13:44,141
- I'll go get you some tea.
- No need.

237
00:13:44,141 --> 00:13:48,341
My Lord doesn't consume
random things from outside.

238
00:13:48,341 --> 00:13:50,700
May I ask,

239
00:13:50,700 --> 00:13:52,608
are these for your own home,

240
00:13:52,608 --> 00:13:55,441
or are they a gift?

241
00:13:55,441 --> 00:13:57,041
What kind of question is that?

242
00:13:57,041 --> 00:13:59,441
Would I come in person
to buy things for the house?

243
00:13:59,441 --> 00:14:01,936
It's a gift, of course.

244
00:14:02,941 --> 00:14:05,208
I heard your shop is very popular.

245
00:14:05,208 --> 00:14:08,274
All the top courtesans in town
love to buy from you.

246
00:14:08,274 --> 00:14:10,975
Whatever is currently in style depends
on your shop's trends.

247
00:14:10,975 --> 00:14:12,102
Is that so?

248
00:14:12,102 --> 00:14:13,602
Oh, sir.

249
00:14:13,602 --> 00:14:15,374
You've come to the right person.

250
00:14:15,374 --> 00:14:16,975
I'm not boasting here.

251
00:14:16,975 --> 00:14:22,677
Last month, two courtesans fought over a set
of orchid-patterned bed curtains from my shop.

252
00:14:22,677 --> 00:14:24,341
Just look at the price they bid!

253
00:14:24,341 --> 00:14:26,952
It went up seven or eightfold!

254
00:14:26,952 --> 00:14:30,440
But I wonder which lady is lucky enough...

255
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:33,270
to have caught your eye?

256
00:14:34,052 --> 00:14:36,075
Qiu Chan.

257
00:14:36,075 --> 00:14:38,777
Qiu Chan...

258
00:14:41,274 --> 00:14:46,316
Miss Qiu Chan from Fenglai Pavilion?

259
00:14:47,475 --> 00:14:50,402
She has bought things from you before?

260
00:14:50,402 --> 00:14:52,374
Of course she has.

261
00:14:52,374 --> 00:14:53,975
That's Miss Qiu Chan!

262
00:14:53,975 --> 00:14:55,541
Though she isn't the top courtesan,

263
00:14:55,541 --> 00:14:57,274
she is still quite famous.

264
00:14:57,274 --> 00:14:59,935
Lately, she's been gaining some many admirers.

265
00:14:59,935 --> 00:15:02,874
You have excellent taste, sir.

266
00:15:02,874 --> 00:15:07,341
Fine. Then tell me,
what kind of fabric does she like?

267
00:15:07,341 --> 00:15:08,774
What style does she prefer?

268
00:15:08,774 --> 00:15:10,465
Well, Miss Qiu Chan...

269
00:15:10,465 --> 00:15:12,975
She has exquisite taste, naturally.

270
00:15:12,975 --> 00:15:16,008
What she likes can only be found
among our shop's

271
00:15:16,008 --> 00:15:20,438
finest embroidered goods
and high-quality silk threads.

272
00:15:31,140 --> 00:15:32,541
You're quite sly.

273
00:15:32,541 --> 00:15:34,141
Since I don't usually visit embroidery shops,

274
00:15:34,141 --> 00:15:37,100
you're trying to fool me
with these inferior goods, aren't you?

275
00:15:37,100 --> 00:15:38,963
Sir, I wouldn't dare!

276
00:15:38,963 --> 00:15:42,408
- These are all our finest goods!
- Finest goods?

277
00:15:42,408 --> 00:15:43,441
Let me tell you,

278
00:15:43,441 --> 00:15:46,700
I've seen plenty of a lady's belongings.

279
00:15:46,700 --> 00:15:48,408
Inferior.

280
00:15:48,408 --> 00:15:50,177
Inferior.

281
00:15:50,177 --> 00:15:51,808
Too inferior!

282
00:15:51,808 --> 00:15:53,340
With this kind of junk in your shop,

283
00:15:53,340 --> 00:15:55,208
how dare you say Miss Qiu Chan visits often?

284
00:15:55,208 --> 00:15:57,210
Move aside! I'll look for myself.

285
00:15:57,210 --> 00:16:02,020
Sir, please, I wouldn't dare deceive you!

286
00:16:03,208 --> 00:16:04,380
Inferior.

287
00:16:04,380 --> 00:16:05,603
Inferior, inferior, inferior!

288
00:16:05,603 --> 00:16:07,441
- Qiu Chan...
- What kind of fabric is this?

289
00:16:07,441 --> 00:16:11,441
- Could he really be a regular at brothels?
- This patten is out of date.

290
00:16:11,441 --> 00:16:14,008
- I'll have to interrogate him later.
- Who would even like this?

291
00:16:14,008 --> 00:16:15,641
This is just too poor.

292
00:16:15,641 --> 00:16:18,363
- Sir!
- Inferior! Inferior!

293
00:16:19,041 --> 00:16:20,808
Why are you following me so closely?

294
00:16:20,808 --> 00:16:22,341
Afraid I can't afford it?

295
00:16:22,341 --> 00:16:23,608
No, sir.

296
00:16:23,608 --> 00:16:25,975
These are all our finest goods.

297
00:16:25,975 --> 00:16:28,408
Even if you don't like them, don't ruin them.

298
00:16:28,408 --> 00:16:30,408
Ruin them?

299
00:16:31,408 --> 00:16:32,475
You two.

300
00:16:32,475 --> 00:16:33,620
What are you just standing there for?

301
00:16:33,620 --> 00:16:34,660
Pick them up with him.

302
00:16:34,660 --> 00:16:36,175
I'll buy everything on the floor.

303
00:16:36,175 --> 00:16:37,841
Take them as my grant.

304
00:16:37,841 --> 00:16:39,641
- Thank you for the grant, My Lord.
- Thank you for the grant, My Lord.

305
00:16:39,641 --> 00:16:42,027
All of them!

306
00:16:42,027 --> 00:16:45,341
Oh my! Sir, you really have a good eye!

307
00:16:45,341 --> 00:16:48,915
- You two, come and help pick them up.
- Shopkeeper, let me do it.

308
00:16:48,915 --> 00:16:50,608
Wonderful.

309
00:16:51,500 --> 00:16:52,700
- This one!
- Look, this one is nice!

310
00:16:52,700 --> 00:16:54,340
- This one is quite pretty.
- Sir!

311
00:16:54,340 --> 00:16:57,836
- How much is this one?
- That's our backyard!

312
00:17:11,341 --> 00:17:12,675
Sir.

313
00:17:12,675 --> 00:17:13,675
Shopkeeper.

314
00:17:13,675 --> 00:17:15,841
I see you have several more rooms further in.

315
00:17:15,841 --> 00:17:18,315
Are all the good goods hidden inside?

316
00:17:18,315 --> 00:17:19,641
How could you say that?

317
00:17:19,641 --> 00:17:21,008
We are open for business.

318
00:17:21,008 --> 00:17:23,141
How could we hide the good goods?

319
00:17:23,141 --> 00:17:24,875
Inside there is just the workshop.

320
00:17:24,875 --> 00:17:27,041
The embroideresses usually work in there.

321
00:17:27,041 --> 00:17:29,141
That's perfect. I'll go in and have a look.

322
00:17:29,141 --> 00:17:31,243
If there's anything good,
I'll buy it immediately.

323
00:17:31,243 --> 00:17:32,441
Please do not.

324
00:17:32,441 --> 00:17:34,574
Inside there are usually only women.

325
00:17:34,574 --> 00:17:35,808
They eat and live in there.

326
00:17:35,808 --> 00:17:38,208
If you go in,
I'm afraid it would be inappropriate.

327
00:17:38,208 --> 00:17:41,941
- Why are you so stubborn?
- My Lord! My Lord, look.

328
00:17:41,941 --> 00:17:43,641
I just picked this one out.

329
00:17:43,641 --> 00:17:45,341
It has two peach blossoms on it.

330
00:17:45,341 --> 00:17:47,361
Does it look good?

331
00:17:51,475 --> 00:17:53,241
Not bad.

332
00:17:53,241 --> 00:17:56,341
To be able to pick out such a fine piece
from that pile of junk...

333
00:17:56,341 --> 00:17:58,341
You're quite something.

334
00:17:58,341 --> 00:18:03,141
No wonder you could coax that girl
into being your sweetheart.

335
00:18:03,141 --> 00:18:06,175
Alright, girl. Go with the shopkeeper
to settle the bill.

336
00:18:06,175 --> 00:18:08,274
Sure thing!

337
00:18:08,274 --> 00:18:11,703
My Lord, you have the money.

338
00:18:15,074 --> 00:18:17,475
This way, shopkeeper.

339
00:18:17,475 --> 00:18:19,941
After you. Please.

340
00:18:19,941 --> 00:18:22,377
My Lord, please.

341
00:18:37,074 --> 00:18:38,608
Fan, you were right.

342
00:18:38,608 --> 00:18:41,208
There is indeed something
wrong with that backyard.

343
00:18:41,208 --> 00:18:43,175
The shopkeeper is definitely suspicious.

344
00:18:43,175 --> 00:18:46,941
The backyard was so quiet.
How could anyone be living there?

345
00:18:46,941 --> 00:18:48,408
Why did you stop me just now?

346
00:18:48,408 --> 00:18:50,541
It would've been better to just
burst in and take a look.

347
00:18:50,541 --> 00:18:51,941
If you had forced your way in,

348
00:18:51,941 --> 00:18:53,341
you would have alerted the enemy.

349
00:18:53,341 --> 00:18:56,930
We'll take the chance
to investigate further tonight.

350
00:19:00,074 --> 00:19:01,208
Fan.

351
00:19:01,208 --> 00:19:03,410
Don't be so anxious.

352
00:19:07,675 --> 00:19:11,141
Since you've already deduced what happened
to Yu Lian, don't keep it from him.

353
00:19:11,141 --> 00:19:13,776
He'll have to find out sooner or later.

354
00:19:15,608 --> 00:19:17,074
Fan.

355
00:19:17,074 --> 00:19:18,741
Based on my deduction,

356
00:19:18,741 --> 00:19:20,975
that embroidery shop is most likely

357
00:19:20,975 --> 00:19:24,341
using the pretense of buying embroidery
at high prices to lure girls there.

358
00:19:24,341 --> 00:19:27,952
Afterward, they trick them
into the backyard workshop...

359
00:19:27,952 --> 00:19:30,608
to sell them off.

360
00:19:30,608 --> 00:19:31,608
Sell them?

361
00:19:31,608 --> 00:19:33,441
Fan, don't worry.

362
00:19:33,441 --> 00:19:35,841
We will do everything we can to rescue her.

363
00:19:35,841 --> 00:19:39,141
In broad daylight,
kidnapping women for brothels?

364
00:19:39,141 --> 00:19:41,408
How audacious.

365
00:19:41,408 --> 00:19:44,574
The backyard was paved with stone,
yet it had subsided so severely.

366
00:19:44,574 --> 00:19:46,441
They must have dug a tunnel.

367
00:19:46,441 --> 00:19:48,408
The girls are sent to the brothel
through a secret passage.

368
00:19:48,408 --> 00:19:50,752
It's completely undetected.

369
00:19:50,752 --> 00:19:54,074
The terrain in Xiangyang
consists mostly of sandy soil.

370
00:19:54,074 --> 00:19:55,608
With this kind of soil,

371
00:19:55,608 --> 00:19:58,341
if a tunnel is dug haphazardly,
it will easily collapse.

372
00:19:58,341 --> 00:20:01,608
I suspect the end of that tunnel...

373
00:20:01,608 --> 00:20:04,475
must be very close to the courtyard.

374
00:20:04,475 --> 00:20:06,408
There's Yulin Alley not far from here.

375
00:20:06,408 --> 00:20:08,675
There's a brothel there
called Fenglai Pavilion.

376
00:20:08,675 --> 00:20:10,594
How do you know that?

377
00:20:11,408 --> 00:20:15,776
I saw it when we went to get our gear
this morning.

378
00:20:17,095 --> 00:20:19,335
Tonight, we'll split into two groups.

379
00:20:19,335 --> 00:20:20,541
One to the embroidery shop,

380
00:20:20,541 --> 00:20:23,208
and the other to Fenglai Pavilion.

381
00:20:23,208 --> 00:20:24,375
I'll go to Fenglai Pavilion.

382
00:20:24,375 --> 00:20:26,794
You're going to a brothel? Can you handle it?

383
00:20:26,794 --> 00:20:29,415
If I can't, do you think you two can?

384
00:20:29,415 --> 00:20:31,608
Anyone can tell that you're a woman
disguised as a man.

385
00:20:31,608 --> 00:20:33,941
Does Zhan look like a patron?

386
00:20:33,941 --> 00:20:35,475
I'm suave and charming.

387
00:20:35,475 --> 00:20:39,241
Getting girls to talk is what I'm best at.

388
00:20:39,241 --> 00:20:42,008
Sir, come in!

389
00:20:42,008 --> 00:20:44,502
Sir, come have a look!

390
00:20:44,502 --> 00:20:46,730
Sir!

391
00:20:47,860 --> 00:20:50,475
Hey, there.

392
00:20:50,475 --> 00:20:52,341
Come in and sit for a while.

393
00:20:52,341 --> 00:20:53,741
[Fenglai Pavilion]
Don't just stand there, sir.

394
00:20:53,741 --> 00:20:56,074
Come in for a cup of tea, sir.

395
00:20:56,074 --> 00:20:57,408
That's right.

396
00:20:57,408 --> 00:20:59,074
Sir.

397
00:20:59,074 --> 00:21:00,141
Come inside and sit.

398
00:21:00,141 --> 00:21:01,875
Lai Fu, hurry!

399
00:21:01,875 --> 00:21:04,465
Sir, please come in.

400
00:21:06,175 --> 00:21:08,136
This way.

401
00:21:13,574 --> 00:21:15,624
This way, please.

402
00:21:23,541 --> 00:21:25,841
Sir, is there a lady you're familiar with?

403
00:21:25,841 --> 00:21:27,860
Call Qiu Chan for me.

404
00:21:27,860 --> 00:21:30,477
Qiu... Qiu Chan?

405
00:21:31,180 --> 00:21:32,820
She's no longer here?

406
00:21:32,820 --> 00:21:36,260
She's here, she's here!
I'll go call her for you right away.

407
00:21:36,260 --> 00:21:40,343
I can't believe someone actually
prefers the old and faded ones.

408
00:22:11,808 --> 00:22:14,693
Sir, Qiu Chan is here.

409
00:22:37,875 --> 00:22:39,274
In recent years,

410
00:22:39,274 --> 00:22:42,327
few guests have asked for
my company for drinks.

411
00:22:45,675 --> 00:22:47,141
Sir.

412
00:22:47,141 --> 00:22:49,204
A toast to you.

413
00:23:03,675 --> 00:23:06,500
Why didn't you save money to redeem yourself?

414
00:23:06,500 --> 00:23:09,241
I was young and foolish, and got cheated.

415
00:23:09,241 --> 00:23:11,975
I ended up losing both my heart and money.

416
00:23:11,975 --> 00:23:14,750
How much is your redemption fee?

417
00:23:22,008 --> 00:23:23,700
Sir.

418
00:23:23,700 --> 00:23:26,028
Have we met before?

419
00:23:26,641 --> 00:23:28,502
What?

420
00:23:28,502 --> 00:23:30,852
Do I look familiar?

421
00:23:41,020 --> 00:23:43,762
I feel like I've seen you somewhere.

422
00:23:45,768 --> 00:23:47,175
Master Hua is here!

423
00:23:47,175 --> 00:23:50,515
Master Hua, you've arrived!

424
00:23:50,515 --> 00:23:52,081
Master Hua is here!

425
00:23:52,081 --> 00:23:54,281
Haven't seen you for days. Why?

426
00:23:54,281 --> 00:23:56,614
Were you busy tending to
that little widow on Qipan Street?

427
00:23:56,614 --> 00:23:58,415
[Hua Chong]
Did she finally give in to you?

428
00:23:58,415 --> 00:24:00,300
What do you mean 'tending to'?

429
00:24:00,300 --> 00:24:03,860
I was there to settle things for her!

430
00:24:03,860 --> 00:24:06,103
- Drink up!
- All right!

431
00:24:06,103 --> 00:24:08,215
Who were you looking for all this time?

432
00:24:08,215 --> 00:24:09,481
Who was I looking for?

433
00:24:09,481 --> 00:24:11,695
So you just kept waiting for me, right?

434
00:24:11,695 --> 00:24:13,848
Yes, Master Hua.

435
00:24:13,848 --> 00:24:16,010
Please, have a seat.

436
00:24:17,481 --> 00:24:19,190
Master Hua, please sit.

437
00:24:19,190 --> 00:24:21,630
Master Hua, have some tea.

438
00:24:22,381 --> 00:24:25,515
Master Hua, you haven't been here
for so long. Where have you been?

439
00:24:25,515 --> 00:24:28,265
Did you go off to some house
to snatch another bride?

440
00:24:28,265 --> 00:24:30,381
Well... You all can leave now.

441
00:24:30,381 --> 00:24:31,715
Oh please, Master Hua.

442
00:24:31,715 --> 00:24:34,827
Get out! I suddenly feel unwell.

443
00:24:34,827 --> 00:24:36,300
What's wrong with him?

444
00:24:36,300 --> 00:24:39,496
Who knows? He wasn't like this before.

445
00:24:42,581 --> 00:24:45,648
Master Bai! Please!
I'll never do it again! Never!

446
00:24:45,648 --> 00:24:48,114
With a face like yours,
how dare you call yourself handsome?

447
00:24:48,114 --> 00:24:50,081
If I catch you harassing women again,

448
00:24:50,081 --> 00:24:51,881
it won't be just a beating.

449
00:24:51,881 --> 00:24:55,170
- Do you hear me?
- I hear you! I hear you!

450
00:24:56,215 --> 00:24:57,314
Master Bai.

451
00:24:57,314 --> 00:25:00,150
Sit, please.

452
00:25:01,781 --> 00:25:04,048
Master Bai, what are your orders?

453
00:25:05,048 --> 00:25:07,515
I don't know if it's because
you're thick-skinned,

454
00:25:07,515 --> 00:25:09,890
but your face healed quite fast.

455
00:25:10,890 --> 00:25:14,190
Master Bai. I've been staying
in the brothels lately.

456
00:25:14,190 --> 00:25:16,723
I haven't harassed a single girl. Truly.

457
00:25:16,723 --> 00:25:18,490
You were shouting so loudly just now.

458
00:25:18,490 --> 00:25:20,950
Do you think I'm deaf?

459
00:25:22,814 --> 00:25:25,340
Hand over all the money you have.

460
00:25:26,614 --> 00:25:28,404
Hurry up!

461
00:25:42,114 --> 00:25:43,381
Take it.

462
00:25:43,381 --> 00:25:45,336
It's for your redemption.

463
00:25:49,981 --> 00:25:51,977
No need to thank me.

464
00:25:53,381 --> 00:25:55,097
Go.

465
00:26:02,181 --> 00:26:03,881
Still looking?

466
00:26:03,881 --> 00:26:05,915
If anything happens to her,

467
00:26:05,915 --> 00:26:08,377
I'll gouge your eyes out.

468
00:26:10,814 --> 00:26:12,581
Master Bai, don't be angry.

469
00:26:12,581 --> 00:26:14,640
Come on, let's drink.

470
00:26:16,248 --> 00:26:19,281
Why did you come to Xiangyang?

471
00:26:19,281 --> 00:26:21,281
You think I wouldn't chase you down here?

472
00:26:21,281 --> 00:26:22,715
So you're here to mess around?

473
00:26:22,715 --> 00:26:25,881
Look at what you're saying.
How am I messing around?

474
00:26:25,881 --> 00:26:28,581
I have a friend who opened a shop in Xiangyang.

475
00:26:28,581 --> 00:26:30,448
I came to recover and help him out.

476
00:26:30,448 --> 00:26:32,648
A shop?

477
00:26:32,648 --> 00:26:34,077
Is it a business of murder and robbery?

478
00:26:34,077 --> 00:26:36,281
Ugh! How could that be?

479
00:26:36,281 --> 00:26:38,865
I wouldn't dare.

480
00:26:41,614 --> 00:26:43,375
Sit!

481
00:26:44,048 --> 00:26:45,381
Look at your face.

482
00:26:45,381 --> 00:26:46,814
What are you afraid of?

483
00:26:46,814 --> 00:26:49,015
I'm just inviting you
over for a drink as a friend.

484
00:26:49,015 --> 00:26:50,827
No big deal.

485
00:26:56,248 --> 00:26:58,481
Look at me being silly!

486
00:26:58,481 --> 00:27:01,648
I thought Master Bai
never visited places like this.

487
00:27:01,648 --> 00:27:02,887
Turns out you're more of a player than me.

488
00:27:02,887 --> 00:27:04,255
You gave so much money just like that.

489
00:27:04,255 --> 00:27:06,381
You've outdone me...

490
00:27:06,381 --> 00:27:11,515
But Master Bai, if you're going to splurge,
pick someone young.

491
00:27:11,515 --> 00:27:15,181
This Fenglai Pavilion was the most popular
brothel in Xiangyang over a decade ago.

492
00:27:15,181 --> 00:27:16,581
But it's no good now.

493
00:27:16,581 --> 00:27:19,681
When it comes to these things,
you aren't one to settle for less.

494
00:27:19,681 --> 00:27:21,790
Why did you choose this place?

495
00:27:21,790 --> 00:27:24,048
You get me.

496
00:27:24,048 --> 00:27:25,381
When it comes to Xiangyang...

497
00:27:25,381 --> 00:27:28,181
honestly, it can't compare to Jiangnan.

498
00:27:28,181 --> 00:27:29,515
I'm just...

499
00:27:29,515 --> 00:27:31,477
making do.

500
00:28:31,900 --> 00:28:35,967
Why are the Hanshui Palace people
with Shao Ji Zu?

501
00:28:44,614 --> 00:28:47,715
His Lordship really has foresight.

502
00:28:47,715 --> 00:28:50,648
But Zhan Zhao still managed to escape.

503
00:28:50,648 --> 00:28:53,583
That night, someone brought a command token

504
00:28:53,583 --> 00:28:56,836
to the Dali Court to secure
Zhan Zhao's release.

505
00:28:56,836 --> 00:28:57,915
What?

506
00:28:57,915 --> 00:29:02,081
Prince Hui brought Bai Yu Tang
to report to His Majesty.

507
00:29:02,081 --> 00:29:06,715
He said, "Zhan Zhao's enemies would seek
revenge in the Dali Court's prison."

508
00:29:06,715 --> 00:29:08,114
His Majesty felt that...

509
00:29:08,114 --> 00:29:10,848
since Zhan Zhao has served
the court for many years,

510
00:29:10,848 --> 00:29:13,215
and has many achievements to his name,

511
00:29:13,215 --> 00:29:16,295
he ordered Prince Hui to take the token
to the Dali Court,

512
00:29:16,295 --> 00:29:19,114
and transferred Zhan Zhao
to the Imperial Prison.

513
00:29:19,114 --> 00:29:20,448
But who would have thought,

514
00:29:20,448 --> 00:29:22,881
that Bai Yu Tang would steal the token midway,

515
00:29:22,881 --> 00:29:26,965
and work with Zhan Zhao
from the inside to flee the capital?

516
00:29:26,965 --> 00:29:29,781
His Majesty clearly let Zhan Zhao go
on purpose.

517
00:29:29,781 --> 00:29:33,314
After that, His Majesty went with the flow.

518
00:29:33,314 --> 00:29:38,448
He said, "Since Prince Hui believed rumors
and let Zhan Zhao escape,

519
00:29:38,448 --> 00:29:40,281
he should redeem himself through service,

520
00:29:40,281 --> 00:29:44,814
and take over from Cheng Hao
to investigate the cases involving Zhan Zhao."

521
00:29:44,814 --> 00:29:47,381
After Prince Hui became the presiding judge,

522
00:29:47,381 --> 00:29:49,535
he first released the rumor-mongers,

523
00:29:49,535 --> 00:29:51,677
which calmed the public's anger.

524
00:29:51,677 --> 00:29:54,481
Then he interrogated the jailer...

525
00:29:54,481 --> 00:29:56,515
sent from Yicheng County.

526
00:29:56,515 --> 00:30:00,620
He concluded that the facts of
the murder case against Zhan Zhao were unclear.

527
00:30:00,620 --> 00:30:03,314
It was too early to convict him.

528
00:30:03,314 --> 00:30:07,381
Then, he announced to the public that
Zhan Zhao would be pursued,

529
00:30:07,381 --> 00:30:10,181
and the trial would resume once caught.

530
00:30:10,181 --> 00:30:15,381
Prince Hui will surely make excuses
to delay issuing the arrest warrant.

531
00:30:15,381 --> 00:30:16,402
Correct.

532
00:30:16,402 --> 00:30:18,715
Cheng Hao urged him several times.

533
00:30:18,715 --> 00:30:23,900
It wasn't until today that Prince Hui
finally issued the arrest warrant.

534
00:30:23,900 --> 00:30:27,207
I'm afraid that by the time it reaches us,

535
00:30:27,207 --> 00:30:31,215
Zhan Zhao will have already
turned Xiangyang upside down.

536
00:30:31,215 --> 00:30:33,515
Should we suspend...

537
00:30:33,515 --> 00:30:35,581
our business here for now?

538
00:30:35,581 --> 00:30:37,314
I came here today...

539
00:30:37,314 --> 00:30:40,614
specifically to discuss this with He Bo.

540
00:30:40,614 --> 00:30:44,081
But he doesn't take Zhan Zhao seriously at all.

541
00:30:44,081 --> 00:30:46,648
That really worries me.

542
00:30:46,648 --> 00:30:48,315
Therefore...

543
00:30:48,315 --> 00:30:52,715
I sent someone to give Zhi Hua a few warnings.

544
00:30:52,715 --> 00:30:55,350
One more thing.

545
00:30:56,181 --> 00:31:00,215
You should rein in your future wife.

546
00:31:00,215 --> 00:31:02,181
She is always with Zhan Zhao.

547
00:31:02,181 --> 00:31:04,681
If His Lordship finds out,

548
00:31:04,681 --> 00:31:07,823
he will be very displeased.

549
00:31:17,114 --> 00:31:19,215
Master Bai, what is this?

550
00:31:19,215 --> 00:31:20,915
Where are we going?

551
00:31:20,915 --> 00:31:23,281
Why are you cuddling me?

552
00:31:23,281 --> 00:31:25,152
Well...

553
00:31:28,415 --> 00:31:29,975
I'll ask you one last time.

554
00:31:29,975 --> 00:31:31,781
Tell me the truth.

555
00:31:31,781 --> 00:31:33,448
What's the secret of this brothel?

556
00:31:33,448 --> 00:31:35,248
There's no secret.

557
00:31:35,248 --> 00:31:36,295
Master Bai.

558
00:31:36,295 --> 00:31:39,448
You can't just say she's suspicious
just because she isn't pretty.

559
00:31:39,448 --> 00:31:41,248
That's not how it works, right?

560
00:31:41,248 --> 00:31:43,614
What is that room behind the stairs used for?

561
00:31:43,614 --> 00:31:46,248
Why did I see so many people
being led straight in there?

562
00:31:46,248 --> 00:31:48,515
Those are just their regular girls.

563
00:31:48,515 --> 00:31:50,515
Of course they'd be led straight in
upon arrival.

564
00:31:50,515 --> 00:31:54,620
Well! So many regulars living together, huh?

565
00:31:54,620 --> 00:31:58,820
Are you trying to fool me
like I'm some brainless idiot, huh?

566
00:32:03,015 --> 00:32:04,452
Don't be afraid.

567
00:32:04,452 --> 00:32:06,602
I won't hit you this time.

568
00:32:18,015 --> 00:32:19,048
What did you give me?

569
00:32:19,048 --> 00:32:21,215
Don't you enjoy a life of debauchery,
Master Hua?

570
00:32:21,215 --> 00:32:24,315
I'm giving you a Tonifying Pill.

571
00:32:27,848 --> 00:32:30,181
Don't waste your energy.

572
00:32:31,181 --> 00:32:32,915
Enjoy yourself tonight.

573
00:32:32,915 --> 00:32:35,048
Come find me at the inn
at the east end of the city tomorrow.

574
00:32:35,048 --> 00:32:36,581
And tell me all about it.

575
00:32:36,581 --> 00:32:40,163
How effective was that pill?

576
00:32:52,415 --> 00:32:53,681
Shao Ji Zu?

577
00:32:53,681 --> 00:32:56,800
You mean he's with the Hanshui Palace?

578
00:32:56,800 --> 00:32:59,881
- Her future husband is quite something.
- I'll say it again, he's not!

579
00:32:59,881 --> 00:33:02,290
I would never marry him.

580
00:33:03,581 --> 00:33:04,781
Let's get down to business.

581
00:33:04,781 --> 00:33:06,448
What did you find out at Fenglai Pavilion?

582
00:33:06,448 --> 00:33:08,314
There's definitely something fishy
about Fenglai Pavilion.

583
00:33:08,314 --> 00:33:11,081
It's run-down and barely gets
any customers during the day.

584
00:33:11,081 --> 00:33:13,681
Yet the tableware they use
is extremely exquisite.

585
00:33:13,681 --> 00:33:15,575
The girls are dressed in fine silks.

586
00:33:15,575 --> 00:33:18,248
These expenses are not something
Fenglai Pavilion should be able to afford.

587
00:33:18,248 --> 00:33:19,481
Most importantly,

588
00:33:19,481 --> 00:33:23,215
I saw many martial arts masters being led
to the same room as soon as they entered.

589
00:33:23,215 --> 00:33:26,899
I think there's more to that room
than meets the eye.

590
00:33:27,648 --> 00:33:29,081
I'll go with you tomorrow.

591
00:33:29,081 --> 00:33:30,715
No need.

592
00:33:30,715 --> 00:33:33,648
Tomorrow, a clue will deliver itself
to our doorstep.

593
00:33:33,648 --> 00:33:35,640
Get some sleep tonight.

594
00:33:37,581 --> 00:33:40,755
Why does this wind chime look so familiar?

595
00:33:41,481 --> 00:33:43,681
The one you made last time was nice,

596
00:33:43,681 --> 00:33:46,935
so I followed your example and made one.

597
00:33:48,381 --> 00:33:49,515
It's hideous.

598
00:33:49,515 --> 00:33:52,414
Do not tell anyone you learned that from me.

599
00:33:55,781 --> 00:33:57,848
Why don't you ask me...

600
00:33:57,848 --> 00:34:00,381
what the clue is that's coming tomorrow?

601
00:34:00,381 --> 00:34:01,915
You said it yourself.

602
00:34:01,915 --> 00:34:03,468
We'll know tomorrow.

603
00:34:03,468 --> 00:34:04,681
Why should I ask?

604
00:34:04,681 --> 00:34:06,015
Well...

605
00:34:06,015 --> 00:34:09,735
If you want to know, I can give you a hint.

606
00:34:10,735 --> 00:34:13,402
Do you want to know or not?

607
00:34:17,248 --> 00:34:19,592
A little.

608
00:34:21,848 --> 00:34:23,614
I went to Fenglai Pavilion today.

609
00:34:23,614 --> 00:34:26,214
I ran into that creep Hua Chong.

610
00:34:26,214 --> 00:34:29,095
He seemed to know Fenglai Pavilion inside out.

611
00:34:29,095 --> 00:34:31,481
I think he must know
the truth about Fenglai Pavilion.

612
00:34:31,481 --> 00:34:33,181
But he wouldn't tell me the truth.

613
00:34:33,181 --> 00:34:35,848
So, I fed him something good.

614
00:34:35,848 --> 00:34:38,081
Just wait and see if he
comes looking for me tomorrow.

615
00:34:38,081 --> 00:34:39,448
What did you feed him?

616
00:34:39,448 --> 00:34:41,415
Doesn't he like to mess around with girls?

617
00:34:41,415 --> 00:34:43,781
Then I'd strip him of his manhood.

618
00:34:43,781 --> 00:34:46,365
Let's see if he can still harm them.

619
00:34:48,015 --> 00:34:49,815
You're just like Ming Zhu Er.

620
00:34:49,815 --> 00:34:52,981
Carrying that kind of medicine
just to play pranks on people.

621
00:34:52,981 --> 00:34:54,515
How is this a prank?

622
00:34:54,515 --> 00:34:56,114
I'm enforcing justice for Heaven.

623
00:34:56,114 --> 00:34:57,681
Regarding the crimes he committed,

624
00:34:57,681 --> 00:35:00,908
when he spoke of them,
he acted like it was nothing.

625
00:35:00,908 --> 00:35:04,681
He said, "I only ruined the innocence
of a few girls."

626
00:35:04,681 --> 00:35:05,981
In this day and age,

627
00:35:05,981 --> 00:35:09,081
can a girl whose innocence is ruined
still find a way to live?

628
00:35:09,081 --> 00:35:11,581
I bet several of them
have already taken their own lives.

629
00:35:11,581 --> 00:35:15,614
His actions are no different from murder.

630
00:35:15,614 --> 00:35:19,114
Instead of waiting for the officials
to find evidence to convict him,

631
00:35:19,114 --> 00:35:20,714
Why not just like what I did?

632
00:35:20,714 --> 00:35:22,048
Castrate him directly!

633
00:35:22,048 --> 00:35:24,907
Pull the evil out by its roots.

634
00:35:31,848 --> 00:35:34,581
Why aren't you saying anything?

635
00:35:34,581 --> 00:35:36,689
Go to sleep.

636
00:35:59,214 --> 00:36:01,415
Master Bai!

637
00:36:01,415 --> 00:36:05,359
I-I-I can't take it anymore!

638
00:36:05,359 --> 00:36:07,181
See? The clue.

639
00:36:07,181 --> 00:36:10,255
Please save me!

640
00:36:10,255 --> 00:36:12,702
I can't take it!

641
00:36:12,702 --> 00:36:14,321
Master!

642
00:36:14,321 --> 00:36:17,381
What did you feed me last night?
It's not proper to harm me like this, right?

643
00:36:17,381 --> 00:36:18,714
How is this harming you?

644
00:36:18,714 --> 00:36:20,881
I'm helping you turn over
a new leaf, all right?

645
00:36:20,881 --> 00:36:23,381
I'm begging you.
You can beat me however you want,

646
00:36:23,381 --> 00:36:26,752
but you can't use this trick on me!

647
00:36:31,214 --> 00:36:33,081
Actually, I don't want to trouble you.

648
00:36:33,081 --> 00:36:34,700
I just want to ask a few questions.

649
00:36:34,700 --> 00:36:36,681
Ask away. I'll tell you everything.

650
00:36:36,681 --> 00:36:39,870
What's the secret of Fenglai Pavilion?

651
00:36:42,620 --> 00:36:44,448
I... I'll talk.

652
00:36:44,448 --> 00:36:46,015
I'll talk, okay?

653
00:36:46,015 --> 00:36:47,866
That Fenglai Pavilion...

654
00:36:47,866 --> 00:36:50,665
It looks like a run-down brothel,

655
00:36:50,665 --> 00:36:54,485
but it hides many secrets underground.

656
00:36:56,248 --> 00:36:57,581
Go on.

657
00:36:57,581 --> 00:36:59,481
There's a hidden paradise underground...

658
00:36:59,481 --> 00:37:02,340
called Zhongxiao Pavilion.

659
00:37:02,340 --> 00:37:04,695
Many stunning beauties are kept there.

660
00:37:04,695 --> 00:37:06,114
It's said that...

661
00:37:06,114 --> 00:37:08,780
one look is enough to make you
lose your soul in ecstasy.

662
00:37:08,780 --> 00:37:11,381
Where were these women gathered from?

663
00:37:11,381 --> 00:37:13,320
Do you know?

664
00:37:13,981 --> 00:37:15,848
I'm asking you. Speak!

665
00:37:15,848 --> 00:37:17,367
That's their business.

666
00:37:17,367 --> 00:37:19,048
How... how could I know?

667
00:37:19,048 --> 00:37:20,981
How does one enter Zhongxiao Pavilion?

668
00:37:20,981 --> 00:37:22,660
A command token.

669
00:37:22,660 --> 00:37:26,776
You need a token issued by them.
You must show it to get in.

670
00:37:30,981 --> 00:37:32,848
You're so familiar with that place,

671
00:37:32,848 --> 00:37:34,315
you must have a token on you.

672
00:37:34,315 --> 00:37:38,315
Master, you flatter me.
I'm just a nobody but a creep.

673
00:37:38,315 --> 00:37:40,420
How could I ever be their honored guest?

674
00:37:40,420 --> 00:37:42,396
I hang around there every day just

675
00:37:42,396 --> 00:37:46,714
hoping they'll show mercy one day, and
grant me a token so I can see it for myself.

676
00:37:46,714 --> 00:37:48,890
But I'm still waiting.

677
00:37:48,890 --> 00:37:53,327
Master! Stop it, I really don't have it.

678
00:37:55,390 --> 00:37:58,190
I-I just remembered something.

679
00:37:58,190 --> 00:38:00,727
If you two want to go in,

680
00:38:00,727 --> 00:38:02,688
you don't need a token.

681
00:38:02,688 --> 00:38:04,355
Fenglai Pavilion has a rule.

682
00:38:04,355 --> 00:38:06,154
For any first-time guest,

683
00:38:06,154 --> 00:38:07,355
state your title.

684
00:38:07,355 --> 00:38:09,688
If the host recognizes it, you can enter.

685
00:38:09,688 --> 00:38:11,955
You are famous out there,

686
00:38:11,955 --> 00:38:14,254
and I'm sure your friend is just as capable.

687
00:38:14,254 --> 00:38:16,903
Why worry about not getting in?

688
00:38:17,555 --> 00:38:21,700
Besides Fenglai Pavilion, is there any
other way to get into Zhongxiao Pavilion?

689
00:38:21,700 --> 00:38:22,883
Another way?

690
00:38:22,883 --> 00:38:24,500
W-What other way?

691
00:38:24,500 --> 00:38:26,840
- I'm not sure.
- You're not sure?

692
00:38:26,840 --> 00:38:30,596
- You're not sure?
- I really, really don't know.

693
00:38:33,654 --> 00:38:34,690
You can go now.

694
00:38:34,690 --> 00:38:37,154
Yep. Um...

695
00:38:37,154 --> 00:38:39,688
Master Bai.

696
00:38:39,688 --> 00:38:42,555
You... You've asked everything
you wanted to know.

697
00:38:42,555 --> 00:38:45,115
What about my antidote?

698
00:38:45,115 --> 00:38:47,525
You want the antidote?

699
00:38:48,654 --> 00:38:51,254
This antidote must be taken
for seven consecutive days.

700
00:38:51,254 --> 00:38:53,488
I'll give you one pill first. As for the rest...

701
00:38:53,488 --> 00:38:56,021
it depends on your performance.

702
00:38:56,021 --> 00:38:59,809
Alright, fine. I'll take my leave then.

703
00:39:03,154 --> 00:39:04,321
Tonight,

704
00:39:04,321 --> 00:39:07,203
we'll go scout out Zhongxiao Pavilion.

705
00:39:11,288 --> 00:39:13,254
Curse you, Bai Yu Tang!

706
00:39:13,254 --> 00:39:16,970
Once you're in Zhongxiao Pavilion,
you're a dead man!

707
00:39:29,154 --> 00:39:31,121
Shao Ji Zu was just here.

708
00:39:31,121 --> 00:39:32,688
Shao Ji Zu?

709
00:39:32,688 --> 00:39:34,221
What was he doing here?

710
00:39:34,221 --> 00:39:36,055
He just wanted me to go back.

711
00:39:36,055 --> 00:39:37,221
But don't worry.

712
00:39:37,221 --> 00:39:39,955
He didn't find out Fan just now.

713
00:39:39,955 --> 00:39:42,955
We only arrived in Xiangyang yesterday,
yet he's already here to test us.

714
00:39:42,955 --> 00:39:44,861
He seems to be losing his patience.

715
00:39:44,861 --> 00:39:46,774
That's exactly what I told him.

716
00:39:46,774 --> 00:39:49,721
I scolded him away.

717
00:39:49,721 --> 00:39:50,721
Oh, right.

718
00:39:50,721 --> 00:39:53,076
What were you two talking about?

719
00:39:53,955 --> 00:39:58,440
That conversation wasn't fit for a girl's ears.

720
00:39:59,440 --> 00:40:01,367
Ugh, Zhan is just protecting you.

721
00:40:01,367 --> 00:40:03,556
He doesn't want to soil your ears.

722
00:40:04,121 --> 00:40:05,488
That man's name is Hua Chong.

723
00:40:05,488 --> 00:40:06,621
According to him,

724
00:40:06,621 --> 00:40:09,254
there is a place called Zhongxiao Pavilion
beneath Fenglai Pavilion,

725
00:40:09,254 --> 00:40:11,102
where many women are imprisoned.

726
00:40:11,102 --> 00:40:14,855
We suspect the embroidery shop's
backyard leads there.

727
00:40:14,855 --> 00:40:17,536
Does that mean... Yu Lian is also inside?

728
00:40:17,536 --> 00:40:19,254
It's not impossible.

729
00:40:19,254 --> 00:40:20,488
Don't worry, Fan.

730
00:40:20,488 --> 00:40:23,561
Tonight, Bai Yu Tang and I will go
to Zhongxiao Pavilion to investigate.

731
00:40:23,561 --> 00:40:24,567
I'm going with you.

732
00:40:24,567 --> 00:40:27,623
You're a girl. Why would you go there?

733
00:40:28,488 --> 00:40:30,152
With a veteran like you around,

734
00:40:30,152 --> 00:40:31,977
I won't be at a disadvantage.

735
00:40:31,977 --> 00:40:33,321
What do you mean, veteran?

736
00:40:33,321 --> 00:40:34,921
- Who's a veteran?
- You are.

737
00:40:34,921 --> 00:40:36,621
You even know where the brothel is,

738
00:40:36,621 --> 00:40:38,460
and you know the name of Qiu Chan.

739
00:40:38,460 --> 00:40:40,455
You even knew that customer just now.

740
00:40:40,455 --> 00:40:42,254
And you say you're not a veteran?

741
00:40:42,254 --> 00:40:43,254
Zhan Zhao.

742
00:40:43,254 --> 00:40:46,141
In order to investigate for you,
my reputation has been completely ruined.

743
00:40:46,141 --> 00:40:47,321
Are you going to do something?

744
00:40:47,321 --> 00:40:50,088
Alright, stop it, you two.

745
00:40:51,088 --> 00:40:53,754
That Hua Chong was being very evasive just now.

746
00:40:53,754 --> 00:40:56,455
I think he's still hiding something.

747
00:40:56,455 --> 00:40:57,888
Since you suspect him,

748
00:40:57,888 --> 00:40:59,615
then Huo Xiao Mei will have work to do.

749
00:40:59,615 --> 00:41:01,608
After he shows us the way today,

750
00:41:01,608 --> 00:41:03,355
let her follow him.

751
00:41:03,355 --> 00:41:04,390
That's not appropriate.

752
00:41:04,390 --> 00:41:05,555
Given Hua Chong's character,

753
00:41:05,555 --> 00:41:07,055
you can't let Miss Huo follow him--

754
00:41:07,055 --> 00:41:08,821
Why are you acting like Shao Ji Zu?

755
00:41:08,821 --> 00:41:11,521
That creep only has some amateurish skills.

756
00:41:11,521 --> 00:41:14,603
You think Master Huo can't handle him?

757
00:41:15,521 --> 00:41:16,688
It's alright, Zhan.

758
00:41:16,688 --> 00:41:18,055
If you don't let me go,

759
00:41:18,055 --> 00:41:21,243
then I'll have to go to the
brothel with you guys.

760
00:41:24,855 --> 00:41:25,855
Alright.

761
00:41:25,855 --> 00:41:27,888
You must be careful.

762
00:41:27,888 --> 00:41:31,615
Even if you can't get any clues,
do not put yourself in danger.

763
00:41:31,615 --> 00:41:33,288
Don't worry.

764
00:41:34,288 --> 00:41:37,577
Don't worry.
I'll stay right here and go nowhere.

765
00:41:51,481 --> 00:41:54,448
So this is what Little Zhu Ge,
Shen Zhong Yuan, looks like.

766
00:41:54,448 --> 00:41:56,215
Something like that.

767
00:41:56,215 --> 00:41:57,681
Even if someone has seen him,

768
00:41:57,681 --> 00:41:59,214
as long as they aren't too familiar,

769
00:41:59,214 --> 00:42:01,223
they won't recognize me.

770
00:42:02,015 --> 00:42:04,114
What about you? Who will you play?

771
00:42:04,114 --> 00:42:06,481
I've decided.

772
00:42:06,481 --> 00:42:08,863
I'll play Shao Ji Zu.

773
00:42:09,768 --> 00:42:13,315
You want to use his token to enter
the embroidery shop's backyard.

774
00:42:13,315 --> 00:42:15,887
We only know there's a Zhongxiao Pavilion
under Fenglai Pavilion.

775
00:42:15,887 --> 00:42:18,681
But we haven't figured out what's fishy
about the shop's backyard.

776
00:42:18,681 --> 00:42:19,848
What about the token?

777
00:42:19,848 --> 00:42:20,915
How will you get it?

778
00:42:20,915 --> 00:42:22,915
I've asked the Beggar Gang's broker.

779
00:42:22,915 --> 00:42:26,915
Shao Ji Zu is drinking on the second floor
of Baihua Tavern today.

780
00:42:26,915 --> 00:42:29,848
I heard from Xiao Tang
that whenever Shao Ji Zu is frustrated,

781
00:42:29,848 --> 00:42:31,415
he goes there to drink.

782
00:42:31,415 --> 00:42:35,181
It seems Master Huo has truly broken his heart.

783
00:42:35,181 --> 00:42:36,415
To swindle the token from him,

784
00:42:36,415 --> 00:42:38,175
how confident are you?

785
00:42:38,175 --> 00:42:40,836
Just wait and see.

786
00:42:55,565 --> 00:42:57,815
- Wait, sir!
- Waiter!

787
00:42:59,614 --> 00:43:00,848
This is for the liquor.

788
00:43:00,848 --> 00:43:02,515
We pay for him first.

789
00:43:02,515 --> 00:43:03,546
Uh...

790
00:43:03,546 --> 00:43:04,895
There is a distinguished guest upstairs.

791
00:43:04,895 --> 00:43:08,043
- They instructed that--
- He's a friend of that guest. Don't worry.
